Information:


Year : September 19, 2013
Genre : Adventure  Quest
Developer : Phoenix Online Studios
Publisher : Phoenix Online Studios
Publication Type : License (GOG)
Language : English, German
Sound language : English
The medicine : not required [GOG]


Descritpion:


The player will help the FBI agent Erica Reed. Many years ago, she lost her brother because of a serial killer who was never caught. Stress awakened heroine strange abilities allow her to see the past of any object to which it touches. This should help you to solve puzzles and catch criminals.


System Requirements:


Operating system : Windows XP / Vista / 7/8
Processor : 2.0 Ghz
Memory : 2 GB
Video Card : ATI or NVidia 1 GB RAM, integrated Intel graphics are not supported
Hard disk : 6.74 GB (all episodes) of free space


Bonus Features:


* Wallpapers
* Soundtracks
* Avatars
* Comics


